Package forager.domain

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cycle
    Cycle contains a link to a VisitMap.
    Dungeon
    Dungeon is used to store the map and to generate node information.
    Line
    Stores a pre-calculated best possible route from one special tile to another.
    Step
    A state class that contains information about each step.
    Tile
    A node class containing information about a tile.
    VisitMap
    Class for storing a map of visited normal tiles and special tiles that have been spent.
  • Enum Summary

    Heuristic
    Enumerator for different A*-heuristics.
